This product includes software developed as part of the Final Degree Project
(Trabajo Final de Grado) "Posicionamiento indoor con WiFi RTT en dispositivos
Android: adaptación de CAE-CNNLoc y evaluación comparativa frente a centroide
ponderado y KNN-DtC" at Universitat Oberta de Catalunya (UOC), 2026.

Tutor: Joaquín Torres-Sospedra.
Responsible Professor (PRA): Antoni Pérez-Navarro.

This software adapts the CAE-CNNLoc architecture originally proposed by
Kargar-Barzi et al. (IEEE Access, 2024) from WiFi RSSI to WiFi RTT
fingerprinting, and uses the public Wi-Fi RTT dataset published by
Matey-Sanz and Torres-Sospedra (Zenodo, DOI 10.5281/zenodo.15391797).

The dataset itself is licensed under the Open Data Commons Attribution
License (ODbL) and is NOT redistributed in this repository. Refer to
data/README.md for instructions to obtain it from its original source.
